In [50]:
def tuwatt(file, juettner_filename_preset="prog_dayahead_{0}_cut.csv", aiva_filename_preset="P_{0}_48h.csv"):
    org_data = load_data_from_KB(file, folder='Datenpool/')
    org_data = org_data.timeseries.data

    start = org_data.index.max() - pd.DateOffset(months=14)
    end = org_data.index.max() - pd.DateOffset(months=2) + pd.DateOffset(days=2)
    org_data['cut'] = org_data.target.loc[start:end]
    
    # read juettner data
    juettner = pd.read_csv(("juettner/"+juettner_filename_preset).format(file), header=None)
    juettner.set_index(0, inplace=True)
    juettner.columns=["target"]
    juettner.index = pd.to_datetime(juettner.index)
    juettner = juettner.tz_localize("UTC")
    juettner = juettner.tz_convert("Europe/Berlin")
    
    # read aiva data
    aiva = pd.read_csv(("aiva/Prognose {0}/"+aiva_filename_preset).format(file), sep=";")
    aiva['date'] = pd.to_datetime(aiva['date'] + ' ' + aiva['time'], format='%d.%m.%Y %H:%M')
    aiva.drop('time', axis=1, inplace=True)
    aiva.set_index("date", inplace=True)
    aiva.columns=["target"]
    aiva['target'] = pd.to_numeric(aiva['target'].str.replace(',','.'), errors='coerce')
    aiva.index = pd.to_datetime(aiva.index)
    aiva = aiva.tz_localize("Europe/Berlin")
    
    # extract current timeframe from original data
    original = pd.DataFrame(org_data.target.loc[juettner.index.min():juettner.index.max()])
    
    # print statistical data
    print("juettner:")
    print(get_benchmarks(prog=juettner.copy(deep=True), org=original, start=juettner.index.min(), end=juettner.index.max()))
    print("\naiva:")
    print(get_benchmarks(prog=aiva.copy(deep=True), org=original, start=aiva.index.min(), end=aiva.index.max()))
    
    # plot the hell out of it
    p = figure(title="Vergleich manuelle und automatisierte Prognose - {0}".format(file), 
               x_axis_label='Zeit', 
               y_axis_label='Last', 
               x_axis_type="datetime", 
               plot_width=1250, 
               plot_height=500)
    p.xaxis[0].formatter.days = '%d.%m.%Y'
    p.xaxis.major_label_orientation = 3.14/3
    p.line(x=original.index, y=original['target'], line_width=2, color=d3['Category20'][20][0], legend='original')
    p.line(x=juettner.index, y=juettner['target'], line_width=2, color=d3['Category20'][20][2], legend='juettner')
    p.line(x=aiva.index, y=aiva['target'], line_width=2, color=d3['Category20'][20][4], legend='aiva')

    p.legend.click_policy="hide"

    boxes = []

    # Sonntage in hellgrau einzeichnen
    if True:
        alldays = pd.date_range(start=org_data.index.min().date(), end=org_data.index.max().date())
        saturdays = alldays[alldays.dayofweek == 6]
        for date in saturdays:
            start = date+pd.DateOffset(minutes=15)
            end = date+pd.DateOffset(days=1)
            boxes.append(BoxAnnotation(plot=p, left=start, right=end, fill_alpha=0.1, fill_color='grey'))

    p.renderers.extend(boxes)
    show(p)
